snippet.title: WashWash - Trailer
snippet.description:
Game link: https://cyanine.itch.io/washwash

Your hands have become incredibly dirty from doing █████████ and you'll have to wash all the █████████ substances of them to continue your work. This is the one time your highly trained legs will not help and you have to rely on your delicate arms which have not seen a workout in years. 
Watch out the bathroom has not been build for humans with your occupation in mind.

Just wash your hands... it's that simple!

Game created by:
János Weyhknecht
Thomas-Chase Scheffel
Marco Serrao
Philipp Stenger
Marvin Spahn 
Nora Al-Shamery
